# Append-only operations log: `union` merge keeps every branch's entries instead of
# conflicting when parallel worktree sessions both append at end-of-file. Built-in git
# driver — no extra config required. Keep wiki/log.md strictly append-only for this to
# stay clean.
wiki/log.md merge=union

# wiki/index.md is GENERATED by scripts/build_index.py and rebuilt on the target branch
# after merges — never hand-edit it, and never run the generator inside a worktree.
# Intentionally NOT given a merge driver here: if index.md ever conflicts, that's the
# signal someone edited it by hand; resolve by rerunning `python3 scripts/build_index.py`.
